com.here.sdk.core.engine

Class SDKOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.sdk.core.engine.SDKOptions

  • public final class SDKOptions
extends java.lang.Object

    Configuration of the SDK. SDKOptions provide an alternative way to set or update the HERE SDK credentials at runtime to initialize the SDKNativeEngine. SDKOptions fields can also be set via application manifest.

      • SDKOptions

        public SDKOptions(@NonNull
                  java.lang.String accessKeyId,

                  @NonNull
                  java.lang.String persistentMapStoragePath)

        Constructs a SDKOptions from access key id, access key secret, cache_path, cache_size and persistent_map_storage_path.

        Parameters:
        accessKeyId -

        Key used for authentication.

        accessKeySecret -

        Secret used for authentication.

        cachePath -

        Path to be used for caching purposes. If it is not set,

        Context.getCacheDir().getPath() is set by default.

        cacheSizeInBytes -

        Desired upper bound of application size in bytes. When cached data exceeds cache_size, least recently used data will be removed. Default value 256MB

        persistentMapStoragePath -

        Path to store persistent map downloaded by MapDownloader. If it is not set, Context.getFilesDir().getPath() is set by default. Note: The MapDownloader is not available for the Lite and Explore Edition. For these two editions, this property has no effect and can be ignored.
